This repository is provided as a minimal public reproducibility package for
TrimMask trimmed-shell isogeometric analysis diagnostics. It includes exported
diagnostic data, CAD geometry files, and a packaged AutoCAD/ObjectARX runtime
build.

No open-source license is granted for copying, redistribution, modification,
commercial use, or incorporation into other software unless separate written
permission is obtained from the copyright holders.

The complete AutoCAD/ObjectARX C++ implementation is not included in this
repository and is available only from the corresponding author upon
reasonable request, subject to project, dependency, and CAD-kernel licensing
constraints.
